{"page_id":"482","title":"CRO Assay Services | Outsource Experiments, WB, IHC, ICC, ELISA","identifier":"services/assay-services","content_heading":"","update_time":"2026-01-17 14:59:11","content":"<section class=\"mb-6 text-center hero-section\"\n    style=\"background-image: url(/media/images/design-guide/hero-people-team1.jpg)\">\n    <div class=\"dark-overlap\">\n        <p class=\"font-large font-weight-bold mb-4\">Outsourcing your experiments</p>\n        <h1 class=\"mb-2\">CRO Assay Services</h1>\n        <p class=\"font-large mb-4\">\n            Boster offers CRO services for research and assay development. We offer standard\n            services for applications and testings such as WB, ELISA, <a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/services/assay-services/ihc-histology-services\" style=\"color:#EA8D28\">IHC</a> and Flow cytometry. We also offer custom assay\n            services both <i>in vitro</i> and <i>in vivo</i>. \n        </p>\n        <div class=\"row list\">\n            <ul class=\"col-12 col-lg-4\">\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n        <a class=\"btn-outline-white\" href=\"/contact-us\">Contact us for a quote</a>\n    </div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"mb-6 double-column content-section\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-4 p-0\">\n                <div style=\"background-image: url('/media/images/design-guide/hero-people-team1.jpg')\"\n                    class=\"h-100 background-cover\"></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-8 p-0\">\n                <div class=\"bg-lightgrey p-5\">\n                    <h2 class=\"font-large text-orange mb-2 topic-heading\">\n                        Antibody Validation Service</h2>\n                    <p class=\"font-medium text-grey mb-4\">IHC optimization and assay development service for research\n                        and diagnostics</p>\n                    <p class=\"mb-5\">Tired of having to validate one more antibody? Boster offers full service antibody\n                        validation. You can outsource the antibody discovery process to us, have us procure (optional),\n                        prep and test multiple antibodies and tell you which one is best suited for your needs. Not only\n                        does this save you time and hassle, we can also do it more cost effectively due to our economy\n                        of scale and close relationships with other antibody companies. </p>\n                    <div class=\"row list\">\n                        <ul class=\"list-unstyled col-12 col-lg-4\">\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n                    <a class=\"btn-orange mr-4\"\n                        href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/services/antibody-validation-service\">Ready to outsource\n                        antibody discovery work? Take me there!</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"mb-6 double-column content-section\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-4 p-0\">\n                <div style=\"background-image: url('/media/images/design-guide/people-hero-assay-western-blot1.jpg')\"\n                    class=\"h-100 background-cover\"></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-8 p-0\">\n                <div class=\"bg-lightgrey p-5\">\n                    <h2 class=\"font-large text-orange mb-2 topic-heading\">\n                        Western blot service</h2>\n                    <p class=\"font-medium text-grey mb-4\">For both traditional Western Blotting & 2D-Western Blotting\n                        protein characterization</p>\n                    <p class=\"mb-5\">Boster offer the best and affordable <a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/services/assay-services/western-blotting-service\">Western Blot custom services</a>. Get custom\n                        services including extraction of total proteins from tissues, construction of premade Western\n                        blots, immunostaining blots with any antibody, quantitative analysis of immunostaining, and\n                        sending high quality digital images.</p>\n                    <div class=\"row list\">\n                        <ul class=\"list-unstyled col-12 col-lg-4\">\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n                    <a class=\"btn-orange mr-4\"\n                        href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/services/assay-services/western-blotting-service\">See Western\n                        blot service details</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"mb-6 double-column content-section\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-4 p-0\">\n                <div style=\"background-image: url('/media/images/design-guide/assay-pippetting2.jpg')\"\n                    class=\"h-100 background-cover\"></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-8 p-0\">\n                <div class=\"bg-lightgrey p-5\">\n                    <h2 class=\"font-large text-orange mb-2 topic-heading\">\n                        ELISA Testing service</h2>\n                    <p class=\"font-medium text-grey mb-4\">Quantification testing service for biomarkers, multiplex\n                        available </p>\n                    <p class=\"mb-5\">Looking to outsource your ELISA experiments? Do it with Boster, one of the biggest\n                        <a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/services/assay-services/elisa-testing-service\" style=\"color:#EA8D28\">ELISA</a> manufacturers. We provide research grade CRO services focusing on academic research and\n                        publishing.</p>\n                    <div class=\"row list\">\n                        <ul class=\"list-unstyled col-12 col-lg-4\">\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n                    <a class=\"btn-orange mr-4\"\n                        href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/services/assay-services/elisa-testing-service\">See ELISA service\n                        details</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"mb-6 double-column content-section\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-4 p-0\">\n                <div style=\"background-image: url('/media/images/design-guide/people-assay-scientist-microscope3.jpg')\"\n                    class=\"h-100 background-cover\"></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-8 p-0\">\n                <div class=\"bg-lightgrey p-5\">\n                    <h2 class=\"font-large text-orange mb-2 topic-heading\">\n                        IHC histopathology Services</h2>\n                    <p class=\"font-medium text-grey mb-4\">IHC optimization & assay development service for research and\n                        diagnostics</p>\n                    <p class=\"mb-5\">From research <a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/services/assay-services/ihc-histology-services\" style=\"color:#EA8D28\">IHC service</a> focusing on academic research and publishing to diagnostic\n                        assay development, Boster Bio can facilitate the transfer of a research assay to lab developed\n                        tests (LDT) and companion diagnostic tests (CDx).</p>\n                    <div class=\"row list\">\n                        <ul class=\"list-unstyled col-12 col-lg-4\">\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n                    <a class=\"btn-orange mr-4\"\n                        href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/services/assay-services/ihc-histology-services\">See IHC service\n                        details</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"mb-6 double-column content-section\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-4 p-0\">\n                <div style=\"background-image: url('/media/images/homepage/homepage-slide-reporter-cell-lines.jpg')\"\n                    class=\"h-100 background-cover\"></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-8 p-0\">\n                <div class=\"bg-lightgrey p-5\">\n                    <h2 class=\"font-large text-orange mb-2 topic-heading\">\n                        Reporter Cell Line Assays\n                    </h2>\n                    <p class=\"font-medium text-grey mb-4\">\n                        Get real-time data with Boster Bio’s ready-to-use \n                        validated reporter cell lines with Renilla luciferase.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"list-style-bullets\">\n                        <li>Exceptional quantitation for mammalian cells</li>\n                        <li>Tight coupling of protein synthesis with enzyme activity</li>\n                        <li>Rapid and reproducible results</li>\n                        <li>Easy to perform assay</li>\n                        <li>No radioactive material handling</li>\n                        <li>Linear range of activity >5 orders of magnitude</li>\n                    </ul>\n                    <p>\n                        Bring Clarity to Your Research with Boster’s Reporter Beacons of \n                        Discovery!\n                    </p>\n                    <a class=\"btn-orange mr-4\"\n                        href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/cells/reporter-cell-lines\">\n                        See Reporter Cell Details\n                    </a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"mb-6 double-column content-section\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div cl